---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const title = "How CamCleans Works | National Cleaning Platform";
const description =
  "Understand how CamCleans connects households, landlords and property professionals with reliable cleaners across the United Kingdom.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} canonicalPath="/how-camcleans-works">

<section class="section">
<div class="container">

<div class="section-title">
<span class="eyebrow">Platform</span>
<h2>How CamCleans works</h2>
<p>
CamCleans is a structured enquiry platform designed to connect people who need reliable cleaning services with independent cleaners operating across the United Kingdom.  
The system focuses on clarity, consistent service standards and transparent communication.
</p>
</div>

<div class="grid grid-3">

<div class="card">
<h3>1. Submit a cleaning enquiry</h3>
<p>
Customers submit a short request describing the property, the service required and any relevant details.  
This allows the system to categorise the enquiry correctly before it reaches a cleaner.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>2. Service requirements reviewed</h3>
<p>
Each enquiry is checked to confirm the type of cleaning required.  
Clear service descriptions help ensure cleaners understand the scope of work before accepting the job.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>3. Local cleaner matching</h3>
<p>
The platform identifies cleaners operating in the relevant area who offer the appropriate service type.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>4. Job confirmation</h3>
<p>
When a cleaner accepts the work the customer receives confirmation along with the service details that were requested.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>5. Cleaning carried out</h3>
<p>
The cleaner completes the service according to the agreed checklist and property requirements.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>6. Service outcome recorded</h3>
<p>
After completion the job outcome is recorded so that service standards remain consistent across the network.
</p>
</div>

</div>

</div>
</section>


<section class="section section-tight">
<div class="container">

<div class="section-title">
<span class="eyebrow">Trust</span>
<h2>Why customers use CamCleans</h2>
<p>
The platform was created to remove uncertainty when arranging professional cleaning services.
</p>
</div>

<div class="grid grid-3">

<div class="card">
<h3>Clear process</h3>
<p>
Every enquiry follows the same structured process from request through to job completion.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Defined service categories</h3>
<p>
Cleaning jobs are organised into clear service types including end of tenancy cleaning, deep cleaning and after builders cleaning.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>United Kingdom coverage</h3>
<p>
CamCleans supports enquiries across the United Kingdom while connecting work to cleaners operating locally.
</p>
</div>

</div>

</div>
</section>


<section class="section">
<div class="container">

<div class="section-title">
<span class="eyebrow">Work with us</span>
<h2>Cleaners can join the network</h2>
<p>
Independent cleaners and small cleaning teams can apply to receive enquiries through the CamCleans platform.
</p>
</div>

<div style="text-align:center;margin-top:30px;">
<a class="btn btn-primary" href="/join-cleaners">
Apply to join the cleaner network
</a>
</div>

</div>
</section>

</Layout>